# Tube-Manager
An Android application that contains YouTube Clients

Apps: Tubular, NewPipe and LibreTube

Site: https://preview--tube-manager-hub.lovable.app/?__lovable_token=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..qRyvu3WZJsa0Sgajb0O9S0FdWUdeUm9IVb0PZy0wL2o/

How to install?:

(Step 1) Download the latest release (Tube Manager.apk) 

(Step 2) Open „Tube Manager.apk“

(Step 3) Click Install

(Step 4) Click Open

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

How to install app via Tube Manager?:

(Step 1) Select an application and click

(Step 2) Scroll down and select a version

(Step 3) Download and open the file

(Step 4) Click Install

(Step 5) Click Open
